The paper addresses a hard benchmark instance for the Simple Plant Location Problem and proposes a new algorithm using automated generation of heuristics. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Operations Research (cs.OR), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories. The use of optimization techniques and heuristics also suggests that the paper may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) sub-categories.
